{"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"getPushToken","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)getPushToken","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"getPushToken","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","title":"getPushToken"},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/getPushToken"},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Retrieves the current device push token."}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","text":"NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"getPushToken","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"return-value","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Return Value"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The device push token as a hexadecimal string, or nil if not yet registered","type":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Returns the APNs device token as a hexadecimal string. The token is used by Apple’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Push Notification service to deliver notifications to this specific device."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The push token becomes available after:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"orderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Calling ","type":"text"},{"code":"registerForPushNotifications","type":"codeVoice"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"User granting notification permission"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Successful registration with APNs"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"level":2,"text":"Example","anchor":"Example","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Send push token to your backend for server-side notifications:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class PushTokenManager {","","    func syncPushTokenIfNeeded() {","        guard let pushToken = Pushwoosh.configure.getPushToken() else {","            Logger.debug(\"Push token not available yet\")","            return","        }","","        \/\/ Check if token has changed since last sync","        let lastSyncedToken = UserDefaults.standard.string(forKey: \"lastSyncedPushToken\")","        guard pushToken != lastSyncedToken else {","            return \/\/ Token unchanged, no need to sync","        }","","        let hwid = Pushwoosh.configure.getHWID()","","        APIClient.shared.post(\"\/api\/push-tokens\", body: [","            \"hwid\": hwid,","            \"pushToken\": pushToken,","            \"platform\": \"ios\"","        ]) { result in","            if case .success = result {","                UserDefaults.standard.set(pushToken, forKey: \"lastSyncedPushToken\")","                Logger.info(\"Push token synced successfully\")","            }","        }","    }","}"]}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/getpushtoken"]}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"role":"symbol","abstract":[],"title":"PWConfiguration","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","type":"topic"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","title":"PushwooshCore","role":"collection","type":"topic"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/getPushToken":{"fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"getPushToken"}],"type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Retrieves the current device push token.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/getPushToken","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/getpushtoken","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"getPushToken","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"getPushToken"}}}